Skill: Dual Wield
Type : Combat Skill

Dual wield skill allows you to hit with a weapon with your offhand.
The higher your dual wield the more often you hit with your offhand.
The actual ability to wield two weapons is based on your dexterity
as compared to the length of the two weapons combined. 

Syntax: wield <weapon 1> - automatically wields weapon in right hand
        wield <weapon 2> - automatically wields weapon in left hand

